    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔总统赌墨西哥大使馆突袭将在国内得到回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ecuador-s-noboa-gambles-mexico-embassy-raid-will-pay-off-at-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺博亚违反国际规则，派警察冲进墨西哥大使馆，这是一场豪赌。到目前为止，他的努力得到了回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ecuador-s-noboa-gambles-mexico-embassy-raid-will-pay-off-at-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 01:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据新法规，澳大利亚杂货巨头可能面临数百万美元的罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/aussie-grocery-giants-may-face-millions-in-fines-under-new-code</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据临时政府审查建议的强制性行为准则，澳大利亚超市巨头可能面临数百万澳元的罚款，这是解决顽固的高通胀引发的全国生活成本危机的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/aussie-grocery-giants-may-face-millions-in-fines-under-new-code</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 01:27:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国部署第二颗美国本土间谍卫星</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/south-kore-launches-second-homegrown-spy-satellite-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国在美国发射的 SpaceX 猎鹰 9 号火箭上部署了第二颗国产间谍卫星，使其能够密切关注来自拥有核武器的朝鲜等国家的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/south-kore-launches-second-homegrown-spy-satellite-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:39:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥要求秘鲁人签证以打击移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-to-require-visas-for-peruvians-in-migration-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥将要求秘鲁人获得签证才能进入该国，以阻止来自南美国家的移民流量“大幅增加”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-to-require-visas-for-peruvians-in-migration-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和法国呼吁在华盛顿访问之前向乌克兰提供更多援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/uk-france-call-for-more-ukraine-aid-ahead-of-washington-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦在访问华盛顿之前警告称，“未能支持乌克兰的代价”，敦促美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊找到国会批准一项 600 亿美元军事援助计划的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/uk-france-call-for-more-ukraine-aid-ahead-of-washington-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥就厄瓜多尔突袭大使馆事件提出抗议，寻求联合国裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-seeks-un-ruling-in-protest-of-ecuador-s-raid-of-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔警方冲进墨西哥驻厄瓜多尔大使馆逮捕一名寻求庇护的高级政客后，墨西哥将向联合国正式起诉厄瓜多尔，两国关系急转直下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-seeks-un-ruling-in-protest-of-ecuador-s-raid-of-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在海上的大规模建设令菲律宾在小岛的扩张相形见绌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-s-huge-sea-buildup-dwarfs-philippine-push-on-tiny-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南中国海的一个小岛象征着这场斗争——和差距——与中国相比，菲律宾在争议水域主张其权利的努力，中国对大部分水域拥有主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-s-huge-sea-buildup-dwarfs-philippine-push-on-tiny-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登盟友反对停止美国向以色列转让武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/biden-ally-opposes-halting-us-weapons-transfers-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的一位参议院盟友表示，美国应继续向以色列提供武器，他拒绝了众议院议员的呼吁，即在对以色列导弹袭击导致加沙七名世界中央厨房援助人员死亡的事件进行全面调查之前暂停武器转让。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/biden-ally-opposes-halting-us-weapons-transfers-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦魅力攻势旨在促进中国关系并遏制出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/yellen-advances-us-china-ties-despite-tough-criticism-on-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦将在北京会见中国央行行长、前经济沙皇，此次访问在加强双边关系的同时对北京的经济政策提出尖锐批评，这是一次微妙的平衡之举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/yellen-advances-us-china-ties-despite-tough-criticism-on-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
